metadata.name: Elise & Ladybug
metadata.description:
''  Once upon a time there lived a fairy girl named Elise in an enchanted forest. Elise was known for her love for nature and all living things. She spent her days wandering the woods, singing to the melody of rustling leaves.
   One day, while she was resting on a leaf, a curious little ladybug approached her. Elise was very pleased with the presence of the ladybug and had great affection for it. Elise and the ladybug were lost in the beauty of nature, shining together.''

It is designed with Blender3d and clo3d programs.
size: 3840x2160
